text:
Visit the original post to see all 2 images from this gallery. 
Street Style is an ongoing series shot by Highsnobiety. This week we’ve shot 14-year old streetwear aficionado Leo Mandella aka Geo Gully. 
Subject: Leo Mandella aka Gully Guy Leo 
Location: London, England
Occupation: Student
Brands: Supreme x The North Face, Supreme, Louis Vuitton & adidas Calabasas
Editor’s Notes: Leo Mandella isn’t reigning back on his Supreme obsession anytime soon, but he is mixing it up with yet-to-be-released adidas “Calabasas” Powerphase sneakers and some LV monogrammed steez
Check out our Q&A with Leo for more on how he cops his A-grade style .
